    "html": "<html lang=\"en-US\" class=\"light\"><head>\n\t\t<meta charset=\"utf-8\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"icon\" type=\"image/png\" sizes=\"512x512\" href=\"https://z-cdn.chatglm.cn/z-ai/static/logo.svg\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"https://z-cdn.chatglm.cn/z-ai/static/logo.svg\">\n\t\t<link rel=\"apple-touch-icon\" sizes=\"512x512\" href=\"https://z-cdn.chatglm.cn/z-ai/static/logo.svg\">\n\t\t<meta name=\"apple-mobile-web-app-title\" content=\"Z.ai - Free AI Chatbot &amp; Agent powered by GLM-5.1 &amp; GLM-5\">\n\t\t<meta name=\"description\" content=\"Meet Z.ai, your free AI-powered assistant. Build websites, create slides, analyze data, and get instant answers. Fast, smart, and reliable, powered by GLM-5.\">\n\t\t<meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"GLM-4.6, GLM 4.6, GLM-4.6-Air, GLM 4.6 Air, GLM 4.5, GLM4.5, GLM4.6, Deep Research, z ai, z.ai, GLM 4.5 AI, GLM 4.6 AI, GLM AI, Chat Z, zai, Chat AI, GLM, z.ia, Chat Z AI, AI chat, chatbot, z.ai chat, free ai chat, free AI, free ai chat no login, GLM-4.5, GLM-4.5 chat, GLM-4.1V, GLM-4.5V, AI assistant chat, AI PPT, AI presentation, AI presentation maker, AI slides maker, AI slides, slide deck, pitch deck, AI deck generator, free pitch deck generator, AI PPT, AI PPT maker, AI for Google Slides, AI for PowerPoint, AI writer, AI writing assistant, AI code generator, full stack code generation, AI full stack developer, claude code, Roo Code, Cline, Kilo Code, OpenCode, Codex, Cursor, GLM Coding Plan, GLM Coding, AI Coding, code writer ai, magic design, magic design tool, AI inspiration board, visual brainstorming AI, chat with AI, AI对话, AI聊天, 聊天机器人, 免费AI聊天, AI做PPT, AI写作, AI编程, 全栈开发, 灵感画板, AI tool, AI helper, AI for students, AI for marketers, AI for content creation, ChatGPT, chatgpt free, Free ChatGPT, gpt chat, Gemini, Grok, Claude, Poe AI, YouChat, Jasper AI, deepseek, qwen, 豆包, 文心一言, AI搜问答, 写作灵感AI, 代码解释工具, PPT思路生成, 如何用AI做PPT, create pitch deck from brief, AI business plan presentation, marketing report slides,